title: THURSDAY 2/11 - Buccaneers celebrate in style
itunes:title: THURSDAY 2/11 - Buccaneers celebrate in style
description:
The World Champion Buccaneers celebrated their title with a boat parade (0:07) and GM Jason Licht (0:26) talked about retaining their top free agents. Chiefs quarterback Patrick Mahomes (0:53) has surgery on his injured foot, while the Washington Football Team locked up one of their QBs for next season (1:41). Plus, Orlando Brown looking to leave the flock in Baltimore (1:27)
